Communicated by:
ProMED-mail Rapporteur Kunihiko Iizuka

[Yellow fever (YF) currently remains active in Nigeria. The above Nigeria CDC situation report states that all 36 states plus the Federal Capital Territory (FCT) have reported at least one suspected case. A mass YF vaccination campaign is currently underway in Nigeria with 12 states involved so far.

Maps of Nigeria: http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/nigeria.pdf and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=6236702,62. - Mod.TY]
